    <stitle>7 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER SERIES - CHANGING THE INPUT SHAFT</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>CHANGING THE INPUT SHAFT</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
            <title>SPECIAL PROCEDURE</title>
            <para>In some cases, it may become necessary to remove only the input shaft due to clutch wear on the
                splines. In these cases, the input shaft can be removed without disassembling the transmission other
                than removing the shifter housing. Removal of the clutch housing is optional.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
